lead_paragraph: Until Sunday's winner-take-all K League Classic clash, Jeonbuk Motors had been the very definition on a 'bogey team' for FC Seoul this season, winning all three league games and dumping them out of the continent's top club competition.

headline.print_headline: Seoul Savour Championship Triumph at 'Fortress Jeonju'
